{
  "stem": "10745.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came to me and asked me-- and now almost begged me-- that I should not report him that he called me Jew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if I would have maybe gone to the Russians, and-- that he is like that and everything else-- so I says, OK, I won't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, which I did not report him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And actually, it turned out better that way, because two years later, the Russians were gone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the anti-Semitism at that time was huge than ever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the-- in time of the Russian, of course, I didn't learn any more Polish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was learning Russian and Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we changed the languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everything was against Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anybody was-- there was in-- any very rich Polish people, they took away to Siberia from our place, though.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because it was a very rich district.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And for the Russians, we said that Jews will become a mensches, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we were people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And me and my brothers were-- of course, they were taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one was taken away right away into the Russian army, and the second one went when they were going back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They asked us if we wanted to go with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father said-- that I remember-- he said, a war is only with the armies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They don't touch civilians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In that way, he was wrong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In 1941, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The law enacted-- is only-- the only thing is, they didn't like to be religious.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they just-- they made all kinds of funny things that you could say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, you know, in a class with a small audience, or anything like that-- God, give us candy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, there was nothing coming around.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
